description: Ministry of City Planning & Water Supply - Order made to approve the acquisition of the immovable property in Vannarpannai East, Nallur D/S/D, Jaffna District for the Constructions under Jaffna, Killinochchi Water Supply & Sanitation Project. Order made to approve the acquisition of the immovable property in Kohiladeniya, Eheliyagoda D/S/D, Ratnapura District for the Constructions under Eheliyagoda Water Supply Scheme. Order made to approve the acquisition of the immovable property in Moragaha Athura, Godakawela D/S/D, Ratnapura District for the Constructions under Godakawela Water Supply Scheme. Errata to the order published in Gaz. Ex. Ord. No. 1951/12 of 26.01.2016 for Notice No. 02 - 297
